## SeisFluid.registerFrontend() method

Register current wallet address as a Fluid frontend.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
registerFrontend(kickbackRate: Decimalish, overrides?: SeisTransactionOverrides): Promise<void>;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  kickbackRate | [Decimalish](./lib-base.decimalish.md) | The portion of FLO rewards to pass onto users of the frontend (between 0 and 1). |
|  overrides | [SeisTransactionOverrides](./lib-ethers.etherstransactionoverrides.md) |  |

<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;void&gt;

## Exceptions

Throws [SeisTransactionFailedError](./lib-ethers.etherstransactionfailederror.md) in case of transaction failure. Throws [SeisTransactionCancelledError](./lib-ethers.etherstransactioncancellederror.md) if the transaction is cancelled or replaced.
